Pedophile Hunter
[[At_least_100_years|A long long time ago]] (It was actually June 16th, 2007), [[7chan|/i/nsurgents]] posted a guide to hunting [[pedophiles]] on [http://www.freechatnow.com/ this website] and other free chat services [[for great justice]]. They pose as 13-year-old [[Jailbait|girls]] and wait for a pedophile to come along and try to pick them up. Average wait time has been reported as under a minute. Once the pedophile was spotted (not very hard), the hunter slowly encircles them with a mildly flirtatious air, eventually posting [http://tinyurl.com/38v6qz/ this picture] as their own. The goal was to get contact information if possible, post it on the thread for later trolling, and then proceed to fuck with them.

==The Bust==
When the hunter was either convinced that he/she wouldn't be getting any more or [[DO NOT WANT|didn't want any more]] out of the pedophile, they would bust the bubble in one of three ways.

*[[Fresh_prince|The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air]]
*An interrogation a la To Catch A Predator
*The following bullshit FBI warning: 
**NOTICE TO CHATTER: The Federal Bureau of Investigation has logged a record of this chat along with the IP addresses of the participants due to potential violations of U.S. law. VIOLATION: Solicitation of a minor. IMPORTANT WARNING: If you think this chat session was logged in error, please state your reasons to the F.B.I. agent currently monitoring this chat and quote the reference number #2334531343. Failure to do so within the next 2 minutes will result in your IP and address being entered into our criminal data base and legal action. <br><br>Your IP address has been logged by the Child Internet Service Protection Agency. Please wait while memory ref code "XXXXX5151" is entered into the database.

==A Bump in the Road==
The administrator, j0hn, has b& the 7channers with the message "Chat's closed due to aids." He's a justice-obstructing fuckoff and must become an hero.

==Obsequies==
As /i/ was in its death throes at the time, one noble anonymous decided to compile a list of phone numbers for great lulz and justice. M0ar will come, as the prank goes on as /i/'s last great act.

==Faggotry!==
